      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y30.8 Var. a (mss. 15, 40, 88, 400, 410 (sec.m.), 2106, 4161):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>zastaiiō drujim</em>. hōm ud urwarām andar hāwan abganišn</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At ... <em>zastaiiō drujim</em>, he has to throw the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> into the <em>hāwan</em>."</ab>
         <ab>Y30.8 Var. b (mss. 82, 2010, 2104, 2109, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4162): </ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>zastaiiō drujim</em>. ēn gyāg hōm ud urwarām kōftan ud hāwan škāftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "... <em>zastaiiō drujim</em>. At this passage he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> and hit the <em>hāwan</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
